prompt_template:
Given the following content about visual/image-based material:

{{content}}

Generate {{count}} image-based questions at {{difficulty}} difficulty level in {{language}} language.

Requirements:
- Questions should describe or reference visual elements
- Include image description or context
- Provide answer based on image analysis
- Difficulty: {{difficulty}}
- Language: {{language}}

Output Format (JSON):
{
  "questions": [
    {
      "questionTypeCode": "image_prompt",
      "stem": "Question about the image",
      "imageDescription": "Description of what the image shows",
      "imageUrl": "placeholder-url",
      "correctAnswer": "Expected answer",
      "acceptableAnswers": ["answer1", "answer2"],
      "explanation": "Why this answer is correct",
      "difficulty": "{{difficulty}}",
      "points": 10
    }
  ]
}
